      "body" : "At this point,  `pindex->pprev == chainActive.Tip()`.\r\nIf there are valid blocks on top of the new tip with more ChainWork, it will be detected during the `ActivateBestChain(state, Params(), NULL);` in `UniValue invalidateblock(const JSONRPCRequest& request)`.\r\nThe signal then gets fired twice (seems to be okay).",
